            "title": "人行預告明日開展8000億元人幣買斷式逆回購",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行預告，明天將以固定數量、利率招標、多重價位中標方式，開展8000億元人民幣買庍式逆回購操作，期限為3個月(91天) 。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15710428-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e9%a0%90%e5%91%8a%e6%98%8e%e6%97%a5%e9%96%8b%e5%b1%958000%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e8%b2%b7%e6%96%b7%e5%bc%8f%e9%80%86%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc",
